    <header>
        <title>mak:action tag documentation</title>
    </header>
    <body>
        <section id="description">
      
      
          <title>Description</title>      <p>If the action URI of a form or deleteLink is more complex, possibly including other makumba tags, the
      action parameter of the form tag can be omitted, and the action URI can be indicated in a mak:action, anywhere
      inside the form tag.
</p>    </section>
        <section id="attributes">
            <title>Attributes</title>
            <p>This tag has no attributes</p>
        </section>
        <section id="example">
      
          <title>Example</title>      <source>
      <![CDATA[
<mak:editForm object="ins" method="post">
    <mak:action>memberView.jsp?person=<mak:value expr="p"/></mak:action>
    ...
</mak:editForm>
      ]]>
  </source>    </section>
